# FitCity — Implementation Plan v3

> **Tech Stack**: Flutter (UI) + Unity 3D (Game World) + Supabase (Backend) + Redis (Cache)
> **Skyline**: Full 3D cityscape | **Architecture**: Hybrid via `flutter_unity_widget`

---

## 1. Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Flutter Layer (Dart) — 11 Screens"
        A[Splash] --> B[Character Creation]
        B --> C[Task Picker]
        C --> D[Home Dashboard]
        D --> F[Task Detail]
        D --> G[Leaderboard]
        D --> H[Profile]
        F --> I[Workout Celebration]
        H --> L[Neighborhood Hub]
        H --> M[Coin Shop]
        D --> K[Streak Recovery]
    end

    subgraph "Unity 3D Layer (C#) — 2 Screens"
        E[3D Skyline City World]
        J[Cruise / Helicopter Mode]
        E --> J
    end

    subgraph "Backend"
        SB[Supabase PostgreSQL + Realtime + Edge Functions]
        RD[Upstash Redis — Leaderboards + Cache]
        FA[Firebase Auth + FCM]
    end

    D -->|"UnityWidget embed"| E
    E -->|"Message bridge"| D
    D --> SB
    D --> FA
    SB --> RD
```

### The Split

| Layer | Screens | Technology |
|---|---|---|
| **Flutter (11 screens)** | Splash, Character Creation, Task Picker, Home Dashboard, Task Detail, Workout Celebration, Leaderboard, Streak Recovery, Neighborhood Hub, Profile, Coin Shop | Dart + Flutter widgets |
| **Unity 3D (2 screens)** | Cyberpunk Skyline City (full 3D world), Cruise/Helicopter Exploration | Unity C# + URP |
| **Backend** | All server logic, data, auth | Supabase + Redis + Firebase Auth |

### Bridge Communication (`flutter_unity_widget`)

```dart
// Flutter → Unity: Task completed, update skyline
_unityController.postMessage('CityManager', 'OnTaskCompleted', jsonEncode({
  'taskId': 'gym_workout', 'streakCount': 31, 'category': 'strength'
}));

// Flutter → Unity: Switch to another user's skyline
_unityController.postMessage('CityManager', 'LoadUserCity', userId);

// Unity → Flutter: User tapped a building
// Unity C#: UnityMessageManager.Instance.SendMessageToFlutter(jsonData);
```

