## 3. Full 3D Skyline City — Unity Architecture

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is **not** a 2.5D sprite renderer. It's a full 3D cyberpunk city world with real geometry, volumetric lighting, post-processing, and a cruisable third-person experience.

### 3.1 Unity Rendering Pipeline

| Component | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **Render Pipeline** | **URP** | Best mobile performance, supports post-processing |
| **Lighting** | Baked GI + 1 real-time directional + emissive windows | Performance-friendly |
| **Post-Processing** | URP Volume: Bloom, Color Grading, Vignette, Film Grain | Cyberpunk atmosphere |
| **Skybox** | Custom procedural skybox shader | Dusk-to-night cycle |
| **Camera** | Cinemachine FreeLook + Virtual Camera | Smooth cruise/orbit |

### 3.2 City World Structure

```
City World (Unity Scene)
├── Skybox Layer (gradient + clouds + stars)
├── City Grid
│   ├── Ground plane (dark asphalt with grid glow)
│   ├── Road network (grid template)
│   └── Districts[] (one per user)
│       ├── Building[] (procedurally placed from task data)
│       ├── District signage (user name, level)
│       └── Boundary glow ring
├── Atmosphere (volumetric fog + neon lights + god rays)
├── Water/Harbor (planar reflection + wave shader)
├── Player (avatar + camera rig + movement controller)
└── UI Overlay (HUD, tooltips, capture/exit buttons)
```

### 3.3 Building Generation (Modular 3D)

```
Building = Base + Body Segments (N floors) + Crown + Details
```

| Category | Style | Materials |
|---|---|---|
| **Cardio** | Sleek modern glass | Cyan emissive |
| **Strength** | Industrial/brutalist | Magenta neon |
| **Wellness** | Organic/curved | Green glow |
| **Sports** | Stadium hybrid | Amber floodlights |

**Height**: streak_count × 5 (capped 500m). **State**: construction (< 7 days), complete, cracked (broken).

### 3.4 Cruise / Exploration Controls

| Control | Input | Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| Movement | Joystick / swipe | Walk/fly avatar |
| Camera | Drag | Orbit (Cinemachine FreeLook) |
| Altitude | Vertical slider | Street Level ↔ Bird's Eye |
| Speed/Cruise | Button + display | Auto-forward at set speed |
| Building tap | Raycast | Glass tooltip popup |
| Capture | Button | Screenshot → share |

### 3.5 Multi-User City World

Each user gets a 200m×200m plot. Plots arranged in grid with roads. LOD for distant plots. Lazy-loaded from Supabase via proximity triggers.

### 3.6 Shaders (URP)

`CyberpunkSkybox`, `BuildingWindow`, `NeonGlow`, `WaterSurface`, `HologramTooltip`, `CrackedBuilding`, `AtmosphericFog`

### 3.7 3D Model Assets

~40 modular building pieces + avatar + props. Source: Blender or Unity Asset Store (POLYGON City, Sci-Fi City Pack, Mixamo animations).

