## 4. Flutter Screens — Detailed Specs

### Screen 1: Splash Screen
`AnimatedOpacity` + `Lottie` animation, auth check → Home or Character Creation.

### Screen 2: Character Creation
Archetype cards (×4), name `TextField`, avatar config. → `PATCH users` via Supabase.

### Screen 3: Task Picker
Category browsing, frequency slider (1-7x/week), live health impact preview. Min 3, max 6 tasks. → `POST user_tasks` + `INSERT streaks`.

### Screen 4: Home Dashboard
Time-aware greeting, level badge, `UnityWidget` mini skyline, today's task cards with streak + progress ring, health metrics 2×2 grid. → `GET v_user_dashboard` + Realtime on `streaks`.

### Screen 5: Task Detail & Health Impact
Task header + difficulty, per-metric health cards, earnings preview, "Start Workout" + "Mark Complete" CTAs. → `complete-task` Edge Function.

### Screen 6: Workout Celebration
Confetti + Lottie trophy, count-up status/coins, health impact message, building growth mini Unity embed. → Response from `complete-task`.

### Screen 7: Global Leaderboard
Time tabs (All/Month/Week), podium top 3, scrollable list, user row highlighted. → `get-leaderboard` Edge Function (Redis).

### Screen 8: Streak Recovery
Broken streak alert, grace days display, shield purchase, recovery cost table, 48hr countdown. → `recover-streak` Edge Function.

### Screen 9: Neighborhood Hub
Name + motto, collective skyline (mini Unity), stats, raid boss progress bar, member list, mayor announcement. → `GET neighborhoods` + Realtime on `raid_bosses`.

### Screen 10: User Profile
Avatar + stats, skyline preview (mini Unity), achievements grid, neighborhoods, share/shop CTAs. → `GET users` + `GET user_achievements`.

### Screen 11: Coin Shop
Tabs (Skins/Colors/Effects/Character), grid of items, preview in mini Unity, purchase flow. → `purchase-item` Edge Function.

