## 6. Backend Summary

> Full backend architecture documented separately in [backend_architecture.md](file:///Users/saksham/.gemini/antigravity/brain/c6cfa096-0565-4880-aaaf-d5fe320abf5d/backend_architecture.md)

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Auth** | Firebase Auth | Google Sign-In, JWT tokens |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | 13 tables, views, triggers, RLS |
| **Auto-API** | PostgREST | Direct CRUD (10 endpoints) |
| **Server Logic** | Supabase Edge Functions (TypeScript) | 8 validated endpoints |
| **Leaderboards** | Upstash Redis (sorted sets) | O(log N) insert, O(1) rank |
| **Realtime** | Supabase Realtime (WebSocket) | Streaks, raids, user stats |
| **Scheduled Jobs** | pg_cron | Midnight streak check, grace reset, mayor rotation |
| **Push** | Firebase Cloud Messaging | Streak warnings, weekly reports |
| **Storage** | Supabase Storage | Avatars, screenshots |

